1) Why Hartree-Fock? The parametrisation of the pseodo-potential is based
 on the results of a HF- calculation results obtained for a CH3 radical
 and C2H4 molecule.
 Systems of this size (i.e.
 10 and 16 electrons, respecively) can be efficiently treated at a correlated
